description: My Card Shop Simulator 3D lets you build the ultimate trading card empire. Buy booster packs, discover rare cards, and attract collectors to your growing shop. Manage inventory, set prices, and watch market trends to maximize profits. Customize your store, complete daily tasks, and rise from a tiny corner stand to a legendary card destination. Whether you love opening packs or running a business, this immersive simulator brings the thrill of card collecting to life.
